title: Heroes - Rifftrax
description:
Previously on Heroes...



What do you get when you cross the first two episodes of Heroes with Mike Nelson commentary? Is it a chicken? Or is it something more than chicken? Perhaps it is that which makes human. Or more human than human. Yes, a Super Chicken.


Here are episodes 1 and 2 of Heroes synced up with the Rifftrax audio. This is dedicated to Riverburn, Xannax, Frisky_Dingo, and other RT uploaders. I do this because I like the convenience of having a synced up file. If you enjoy this, I highly recommend donating (http://rifftrax.com/donate) or even buying and synchronizing your own Rifftrax. They are a small company and do need people to actually pay for stuff on occasion.



Excelsior!
